57 inline void setToHome(moveit::core::RobotState& panda_state)
58 {
59  panda_state.setToDefaultValues();
60  double joint2 = -0.785;
61  double joint4 = -2.356;
62  double joint6 = 1.571;
63  double joint7 = 0.785;
64  panda_state.setJointPositions("panda_joint2", &joint2);
65  panda_state.setJointPositions("panda_joint4", &joint4);
66  panda_state.setJointPositions("panda_joint6", &joint6);
67  panda_state.setJointPositions("panda_joint7", &joint7);
68  panda_state.update();
69 }

71 class BulletCollisionDetectionTester : public testing::Test
72 {
73 protected:
74  void SetUp() override
75  {
76  robot_model_ = moveit::core::loadTestingRobotModel("panda");
77  robot_model_ok_ = static_cast<bool>(robot_model_);
78 
79  acm_ = std::make_shared<collision_detection::AllowedCollisionMatrix>();
80  // Use default collision operations in the SRDF to setup the acm
81  const std::vector<std::string>& collision_links = robot_model_->getLinkModelNamesWithCollisionGeometry();
82  acm_->setEntry(collision_links, collision_links, false);
83 
84  // allow collisions for pairs that have been disabled
85  const std::vector<srdf::Model::DisabledCollision>& dc = robot_model_->getSRDF()->getDisabledCollisionPairs();
86  for (const srdf::Model::DisabledCollision& it : dc)
87  acm_->setEntry(it.link1_, it.link2_, true);
88 
89  cenv_ = std::make_shared<collision_detection::CollisionEnvBullet>(robot_model_);
90 
91  robot_state_ = std::make_shared<moveit::core::RobotState>(robot_model_);
92 
93  setToHome(*robot_state_);
94  }
95

112 void addCollisionObjects(cb::BulletCastBVHManager& checker)
113 {
115  // Add static box to checker
117  shapes::ShapePtr static_box(new shapes::Box(1, 1, 1));
118  Eigen::Isometry3d static_box_pose;
119  static_box_pose.setIdentity();
120 
121  std::vector<shapes::ShapeConstPtr> obj1_shapes;
122  cb::AlignedVector<Eigen::Isometry3d> obj1_poses;
123  std::vector<cb::CollisionObjectType> obj1_types;
124  obj1_shapes.push_back(static_box);
125  obj1_poses.push_back(static_box_pose);
126  obj1_types.push_back(cb::CollisionObjectType::USE_SHAPE_TYPE);
127 
128  cb::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr cow_1(new cb::CollisionObjectWrapper(
129  "static_box_link", collision_detection::BodyType::WORLD_OBJECT, obj1_shapes, obj1_poses, obj1_types));
130  checker.addCollisionObject(cow_1);
131 
133  // Add moving box to checker
135  shapes::ShapePtr moving_box(new shapes::Box(0.2, 0.2, 0.2));
136  Eigen::Isometry3d moving_box_pose;
137 
138  moving_box_pose.setIdentity();
139  moving_box_pose.translation() = Eigen::Vector3d(0.5, -0.5, 0);
140 
141  std::vector<shapes::ShapeConstPtr> obj2_shapes;
142  cb::AlignedVector<Eigen::Isometry3d> obj2_poses;
143  std::vector<cb::CollisionObjectType> obj2_types;
144  obj2_shapes.push_back(moving_box);
145  obj2_poses.push_back(moving_box_pose);
146  obj2_types.push_back(cb::CollisionObjectType::USE_SHAPE_TYPE);
147 
148  cb::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr cow_2(new cb::CollisionObjectWrapper(
149  "moving_box_link", collision_detection::BodyType::WORLD_OBJECT, obj2_shapes, obj2_poses, obj2_types));
150  checker.addCollisionObject(cow_2);
151 }

153 void addCollisionObjectsMesh(cb::BulletCastBVHManager& checker)
154 {
156  // Add static box to checker
158  shapes::ShapePtr static_box(new shapes::Box(0.3, 0.3, 0.3));
159  Eigen::Isometry3d static_box_pose;
160  static_box_pose.setIdentity();
161 
162  std::vector<shapes::ShapeConstPtr> obj1_shapes;
163  cb::AlignedVector<Eigen::Isometry3d> obj1_poses;
164  std::vector<cb::CollisionObjectType> obj1_types;
165  obj1_shapes.push_back(static_box);
166  obj1_poses.push_back(static_box_pose);
167  obj1_types.push_back(cb::CollisionObjectType::USE_SHAPE_TYPE);
168 
169  cb::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr cow_1(new cb::CollisionObjectWrapper(
170  "static_box_link", collision_detection::BodyType::WORLD_OBJECT, obj1_shapes, obj1_poses, obj1_types));
171  checker.addCollisionObject(cow_1);
173  // Add moving mesh to checker
175 
176  std::vector<shapes::ShapeConstPtr> obj2_shapes;
177  cb::AlignedVector<Eigen::Isometry3d> obj2_poses;
178  std::vector<cb::CollisionObjectType> obj2_types;
179 
180  obj1_poses.push_back(static_box_pose);
181  obj1_types.push_back(cb::CollisionObjectType::USE_SHAPE_TYPE);
182 
183  Eigen::Isometry3d s_pose;
184  s_pose.setIdentity();
185 
186  std::string kinect = "package://moveit_resources_panda_description/meshes/collision/hand.stl";
187  auto s = std::shared_ptr<shapes::Shape>{ shapes::createMeshFromResource(kinect) };
188  obj2_shapes.push_back(s);
189  obj2_types.push_back(cb::CollisionObjectType::CONVEX_HULL);
190  obj2_poses.push_back(s_pose);
191 
192  cb::CollisionObjectWrapperPtr cow_2(new cb::CollisionObjectWrapper(
193  "moving_box_link", collision_detection::BodyType::WORLD_OBJECT, obj2_shapes, obj2_poses, obj2_types));
194  checker.addCollisionObject(cow_2);
195 }

197 void runTest(cb::BulletCastBVHManager& checker, collision_detection::CollisionResult& result,
198  std::vector<collision_detection::Contact>& result_vector, Eigen::Isometry3d& start_pos,
199  Eigen::Isometry3d& end_pos)
200 {
202  // Test when object is inside another
204  checker.setActiveCollisionObjects({ "moving_box_link" });
205  checker.setContactDistanceThreshold(0.1);
206 
207  // Set the collision object transforms
208  checker.setCollisionObjectsTransform("static_box_link", Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity());
209  checker.setCastCollisionObjectsTransform("moving_box_link", start_pos, end_pos);
210 
211  // Perform collision check
212  collision_detection::CollisionRequest request;
213  request.contacts = true;
214  // cb::ContactResultMap result;
215  checker.contactTest(result, request, nullptr, false);
216 
217  for (const auto& contacts_all : result.contacts)
218  {
219  for (const auto& contact : contacts_all.second)
220  {
221  result_vector.push_back(contact);
222  }
223  }
224 }

226 // TODO(j-petit): Add continuous to continuous collision checking
228 TEST_F(BulletCollisionDetectionTester, DISABLED_ContinuousCollisionSelf)
229 {
230  collision_detection::CollisionRequest req;
231  collision_detection::CollisionResult res;
232 
233  moveit::core::RobotState state1(robot_model_);
234  moveit::core::RobotState state2(robot_model_);
235 
236  setToHome(state1);
237  double joint2 = 0.15;
238  double joint4 = -3.0;
239  double joint5 = -0.8;
240  double joint7 = -0.785;
241  state1.setJointPositions("panda_joint2", &joint2);
242  state1.setJointPositions("panda_joint4", &joint4);
243  state1.setJointPositions("panda_joint5", &joint5);
244  state1.setJointPositions("panda_joint7", &joint7);
245  state1.update();
246 
247  cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res, state1, *acm_);
248  ASSERT_FALSE(res.collision);
249  res.clear();
250 
251  setToHome(state2);
252  double joint_5_other = 0.8;
253  state2.setJointPositions("panda_joint2", &joint2);
254  state2.setJointPositions("panda_joint4", &joint4);
255  state2.setJointPositions("panda_joint5", &joint_5_other);
256  state2.setJointPositions("panda_joint7", &joint7);
257  state2.update();
258 
259  cenv_->checkSelfCollision(req, res, state2, *acm_);
260  ASSERT_FALSE(res.collision);
261  res.clear();
262 
263  ROS_INFO_STREAM("Continous to continous collisions are not supported yet, therefore fail here.");
264  ASSERT_TRUE(res.collision);
265  res.clear();
266 }

269 TEST_F(BulletCollisionDetectionTester, ContinuousCollisionWorld)
270 {
271  collision_detection::CollisionRequest req;
272  req.contacts = true;
273  req.max_contacts = 10;
274  collision_detection::CollisionResult res;
275 
276  moveit::core::RobotState state1(robot_model_);
277  moveit::core::RobotState state2(robot_model_);
278 
279  setToHome(state1);
280  state1.update();
281 
282  setToHome(state2);
283  double joint_2{ 0.05 };
284  double joint_4{ -1.6 };
285  state2.setJointPositions("panda_joint2", &joint_2);
286  state2.setJointPositions("panda_joint4", &joint_4);
287  state2.update();
288 
289  cenv_->checkRobotCollision(req, res, state1, state2, *acm_);
290  ASSERT_FALSE(res.collision);
291  res.clear();
292 
293  // Adding the box which is not in collision with the individual states but with the casted one.
294  shapes::Shape* shape = new shapes::Box(0.1, 0.1, 0.1);
295  shapes::ShapeConstPtr shape_ptr(shape);
296 
297  Eigen::Isometry3d pos{ Eigen::Isometry3d::Identity() };
298  pos.translation().x() = 0.43;
299  pos.translation().y() = 0;
300  pos.translation().z() = 0.55;
301  cenv_->getWorld()->addToObject("box", shape_ptr, pos);
302 
303  cenv_->checkRobotCollision(req, res, state1, *acm_);
304  ASSERT_FALSE(res.collision);
305  res.clear();
306 
307  cenv_->checkRobotCollision(req, res, state2, *acm_);
308  ASSERT_FALSE(res.collision);
309  res.clear();
310 
311  cenv_->checkRobotCollision(req, res, state1, state2, *acm_);
312  ASSERT_TRUE(res.collision);
313  ASSERT_EQ(res.contact_count, 4u);
314  // test contact types
315  for (auto& contact_pair : res.contacts)
316  {
317  for (collision_detection::Contact& contact : contact_pair.second)
318  {
319  collision_detection::BodyType contact_type1 = contact.body_name_1 == "box" ?
320  collision_detection::BodyType::WORLD_OBJECT :
321  collision_detection::BodyType::ROBOT_LINK;
322  collision_detection::BodyType contact_type2 = contact.body_name_2 == "box" ?
323  collision_detection::BodyType::WORLD_OBJECT :
324  collision_detection::BodyType::ROBOT_LINK;
325  ASSERT_EQ(contact.body_type_1, contact_type1);
326  ASSERT_EQ(contact.body_type_2, contact_type2);
327  }
328  }
329  res.clear();
330 }

332 TEST(ContinuousCollisionUnit, BulletCastBVHCollisionBoxBoxUnit)
333 {
334  collision_detection::CollisionResult result;
335  std::vector<collision_detection::Contact> result_vector;
336 
337  Eigen::Isometry3d start_pos, end_pos;
338  start_pos.setIdentity();
339  start_pos.translation().x() = -2;
340  end_pos.setIdentity();
341  end_pos.translation().x() = 2;
342 
343  cb::BulletCastBVHManager checker;
344  addCollisionObjects(checker);
345  runTest(checker, result, result_vector, start_pos, end_pos);
346 
347  ASSERT_TRUE(result.collision);
348  EXPECT_NEAR(result_vector[0].depth, -0.6, 0.001);
349  EXPECT_NEAR(result_vector[0].percent_interpolation, 0.6, 0.001);
350 }

352 TEST(ContinuousCollisionUnit, BulletCastMeshVsBox)
